This Document is guide for Updating and Upgrading the Kali Linux Packages
Reference: https://www.kali.org/docs/general-use/updating-a-package/

*********************To update all packages on Kali Linux, you can run the following commands in the terminal*********************
kali@kali:~$ sudo apt update                   # This command updates the packages list.
kali@kali:~$ sudo apt full-upgrade             # Upgrades all installed packages to their latest versions.

*********************Upgrading Specific Packages*********************
kali@kali:~$ sudo apt install --only-upgrade package_name

